LanguageData.JRWHolcorobeusReconstruct.description:
-- > INGEN INTERNAL CASE FILE #02739-1992 [HOLCOROBEUS ATROSULCATUS] CODENAME: HERCULES >380
A large extinct rhinoceros beetle that has a brilliant purple hue. Primitive, but gentle, they have often been used as hauling animals after their introduction on the rim.
